						<summary>

						<p>Built in at the left end. Records the gift of 25 sheep and also a hanging lamp weighing 25 (?) by a shepherd Bhūtan Peṟṟān for burning a twilight lamp to the deity at Malaiyaḍikuruchchi, a southern hamlet, of Śri Pirāntakach-chaturvēdimaṅgalam.</p>						

